Everytime someone we went to school with does better than us a small part of us will die

00:02:54.140 --> 00:02:58.640
we should therefore take immense care to attend very ordinary schools

00:02:58.800 --> 00:03:04.200
and after graduation 
to throw all invitations to reunions straight in the trash

00:03:04.800 --> 00:03:05.680
Thirdly

00:03:09.420 --> 00:03:14.260
A lot depends on what kind of affection we were the recipients of in childhood

00:03:14.500 --> 00:03:18.600
in particular how many conditions our love came attached with.

00:03:19.140 --> 00:03:23.700
Some of us had parets who only knew how to give out the conditional kind of love.

00:03:24.160 --> 00:03:26.640
It was all about the grades and the school reports.

00:03:26.900 --> 00:03:32.020
We therefore grow up of course to be high achievers but it's not so easy, running around

00:03:32.020 --> 00:03:36.540
your whole life long desperate to put out the raging fires of self-hatred

00:03:36.700 --> 00:03:43.900
striving to impress everyone you meet in search of an unsatisfied desire for a parental approval you never knew.

00:03:44.440 --> 00:03:48.700
But others the blessed ones who've know unconditional love, from the start

00:03:48.940 --> 00:03:54.620
will be ok just to be, they won't have to do quite so much pushing they have an inner basic

00:03:54.620 --> 00:03:59.440
buoyancy quaranteed by the knowledge that they once mattered immeasurably

00:03:59.800 --> 00:04:06.060
A big reversal like being fired will be unpleasant it won't necessarily have to be a tragedy.

00:04:08.540 --> 00:04:12.320
Knowing about the odd internal origins of self-esteem is crucial

00:04:12.560 --> 00:04:16.920
because of how often we pursue goals in the belief that success will at last

00:04:16.920 --> 00:04:22.120
give us the keys to feeling good about ourselves. It seem the truth is slightly darker

00:04:22.400 --> 00:04:26.740
you might ostensibly be doing very well at work but if your dad was a big shot

00:04:26.740 --> 00:04:30.540
or your school buddy became president or your parents didn't tank you up

00:04:30.540 --> 00:04:34.840
with the right unconditional sort of love no amount of striving, goalscoring

00:04:34.840 --> 00:04:37.760
and medal-winning is ever really gonna do it.

00:04:38.260 --> 00:04:41.420
This changes where we should imagine our challenges
lie

